var EventDataBinding = require("./event");
 
/**
 */
 
module.exports = EventDataBinding.extend({
 
  /**
   */
 
  event: "keydown",
 
  /**
   */
 
  keyCodes: [],
 
  /**
   */
 
  _onEvent: function(event) {
 
    if (!~this.keyCodes.indexOf(event.keyCode)) {
      return;
    }
 
    EventDataBinding.prototype._onEvent.apply(this, arguments);
  }
});
